## Luồng xử lý chính

```
Upload PDF → S3 → Orchestrator Lambda → Step Functions:
  Extract (pdfjs → Textract fallback)
  → Parallel [ Translate chunks (concurrency=5) | LaTeX normalize ]
  → Merge → Markdown song ngữ → S3 Results
  → Ingest Lambda: embed (Gemini) → upsert Qdrant
→ Frontend polling → hiển thị kết quả + RAG chat
```

